Package com.jackmeng.tailwind

Class use_TailwindTrack

java.lang.Object
com.jackmeng.tailwind.use_TailwindTrack
All Implemented Interfaces:
impl_Identifiable, Serializable
public final class use_TailwindTrack extends Object implements impl_Identifiable, Serializable
A very low level yet concrete definition of a MusicTrack which can be used and parsed by a impl_Tailwind implementation to read data acquired from this file.
NOTE: Data is not directly streamed from this object!
Author:
Jack Meng
